headline: Promotions Drive Black Friday Weekend Gains, Retailers Stay Upbeat on Season
summary: A spike in online shopping and sufficient turnouts in the malls, outlets and urban shopping districts over Black Friday weekend portend a healthy stretch ahead in the days leading to Christmas.

headline: December Is Best For Stocks But Prepare For January 6
summary: December is the best month for stocks, but expect potential profit-taking in the first week of January. Read why investors should focus on stock picking.
